---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Lipo Plus | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Comprehensive lipotropic blend to complement healthy habits.", "canonical": "/services/vitamin-injections/lipo-plus", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate bg-neutral-950 text-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pt-16 pb-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Lipo Plus</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-white/80 text-lg">Comprehensive lipotropic blend to complement healthy habits.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-20 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <article class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-10">
      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Overview</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">
          This treatment is designed to deliver noticeable yet natural support with a focus on safety, efficacy, and patient education.
          During your visit we evaluate your goals, tailor a plan, and guide you through what to expect before, during, and after treatment.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Benefits</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Personalized plan aligned to your goals.</li>
          <li>Evidence‑informed protocols and quality sourcing.</li>
          <li>Clear aftercare guidance and realistic timelines.</li>
          <li>Performed by trained professionals.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Ideal Candidates &amp; Considerations</h3>
        <div class="mt-2 space-y-2 text-white/80">
          <p>Good candidates are generally healthy and have realistic expectations. Some conditions, medications, or allergies may require adjustments or make a treatment unsuitable.</p>
          <p><strong>Not medical advice:</strong> Always discuss your medical history and current medications with the provider.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">How It Works</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80">We combine assessment and tailored dosing to support your goals. The approach varies by indication and baseline status.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Timeline &amp; Results</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Visits are typically brief; series or maintenance may be recommended.</li>
          <li>Individual responses vary; your provider will outline expectations.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Aftercare</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-white/80 list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Follow in‑clinic guidance specific to your treatment.</li>
          <li>Hydration and balanced nutrition support outcomes.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">FAQs</h3>
        <div class="mt-3 space-y-4 text-white/80">
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">How often should I get this?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Frequency depends on goals and baseline levels. Your provider will tailor a schedule.</p>
          </details>
          <details class="group rounded-lg border border-white/10 p-4">
            <summary class="font-medium text-white cursor-pointer">Any downtime?</summary>
            <p class="mt-2">Minimal; brief local tenderness is possible and typically resolves quickly.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </section>

      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">*Informational only; not medical advice. Individual responses vary.</p>
    </article>

    <aside class="space-y-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-neutral-900 p-6">
        <h4 class="text-base font-semibold">Quick Facts</h4>
        <dl class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-white/80">
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Session length</dt><dd>~10–30 minutes</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Discomfort</dt><dd>Minimal</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Downtime</dt><dd>None to minimal</dd></div>
          <div class="flex justify-between"><dt class="text-white/70">Maintenance</dt><dd>Personalized</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
